text: Oktyabrsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Duvansky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 220 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 65 km from Mesyagutovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Oktyabrsky, Duvansky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
